OL,3,CSpare #9.5million? Historic 12th
OL,4,Ccentury castle goes up for sale
OL,6,FAn iconic 12th century castle has been
OL,7,Fput up for sale for #9.5million
OL,8,Ffeaturing 22 bedrooms and 19 bathrooms.
OL,10,FAppleby Castle is described as the
OL,11,Fjewel in the Eden Valley.
OL,13,FLocated on the edge of the Lake
OL,14,FDistrict the castle is set amongst 25
OL,15,Facres of enclosed parkland.
OL,17,FThe Grade I listed building features a
OL,18,F12th century motte and 13th century
OL,19,Fround tower. Tennis courts and fishing
OL,20,Frights on the River Eden are also
OL,21,Fonsite.
