OL,6,FThe main building also features a
OL,7,Fsauna, gym, hot tub, and a games room.
OL,9,FSally Nightingale is the current owner
OL,10,Fof the castle. She has fond memories
OL,11,Fof owning it and is sad to be passing
OL,12,Fthe keys on.
OL,14,FShe said: "We have done quite a lot
OL,15,Fsince I have been here. It has been a
OL,16,Fbit of labour of love to tell you the
OL,17,Ftruth.
